subSubSection.paragraph: Presence of the species in Norway mentioned in Viitanen (2018) without further details; here, we publish the collection data of that record. Uncertain presence of the species in the United Kingdom (Scotland) mentioned in Kramer 2018 ; here, we confirm the identification of that specimen and the presence of the species in the United Kingdom.
